ue,"","Distributed Training","分布式训练技术与框架，包括 DeepSpeed、FSDP、Megatron-Core 等大规模模型训练方案。","_ai/distributed.md",{"type":183,"children":184,"toc":373},"root",[185,194,201,207,238,244,249,276,282,287,314,320,325,344,349,354],{"type":186,"tag":187,"props":188,"children":190},"element","h1",{"id":189},"分布式-distributed-training",[191],{"type":192,"value":193},"text","分布式 (Distributed Training)",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":196,"children":198},"h2",{"id":197},"deepspeedzero-优化器的显存革命",[199],{"type":192,"value":200},"DeepSpeed：ZeRO 优化器的显存革命",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":203,"children":204},"p",{},[205],{"type":192,"value":206},"DeepSpeed 是微软开源的深度学习优化库，核心是 ZeRO（Zero Redundancy Optimizer）技术。通过三个阶段逐步释放显存压力：ZeRO-1 优化器状态分片节省 4x 显存，ZeRO-2 梯度分片再节省 2x，ZeRO-3 参数分片再节省 2x 并支持单卡加载超大模型。它是训练 100B+ 参数模型的首选方案，支持流水线并行、张量并行与 ZeRO 的组合。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":208,"children":209},{},[210,212,221,223,230,231],{"type":192,"value":211},"见：",{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":214,"children":218},"a",{"href":215,"rel":216},"https://github.com/deepspeedai/DeepSpeed",[217],"nofollow",[219],{"type":192,"value":220},"DeepSpeed GitHub",{"type":192,"value":222}," | ",{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":224,"children":227},{"href":225,"rel":226},"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/zero-deepspeed-new-system-optimizations-enable-training-models-with-over-100-billion-parameters/",[217],[228],{"type":192,"value":229},"ZeRO 论文",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":232,"children":235},{"href":233,"rel":234},"https://www.deepspeed.ai/",[217],[236],{"type":192,"value":237},"DeepSpeed 官网",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":239,"children":241},{"id":240},"fsdppytorch-原生全分片数据并行",[242],{"type":192,"value":243},"FSDP：PyTorch 原生全分片数据并行",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":245,"children":246},{},[247],{"type":192,"value":248},"FSDP（Fully Sharded Data Parallel）是 PyTorch 官方的大模型分布式方案，设计理念与 DeepSpeed ZeRO-3 类似，但集成更紧密。它将模型参数、梯度和优化器状态分片到多个 GPU 上，在保持通信开销不变的同时显著降低单卡内存占用。API 简洁，与 PyTorch 生态无缝集成，适合快速迭代的研究场景。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":250,"children":251},{},[252,253,260,261,268,269],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":254,"children":257},{"href":255,"rel":256},"https://docs.pytorch.org/tutorials/intermediate/FSDP_advanced_tutorial.html",[217],[258],{"type":192,"value":259},"PyTorch FSDP 文档",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":262,"children":265},{"href":263,"rel":264},"https://pytorch.org/blog/introducing-pytorch-fully-sharded-data-parallel-api/",[217],[266],{"type":192,"value":267},"FSDP 介绍",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":270,"children":273},{"href":271,"rel":272},"https://huggingface.co/docs/accelerate/en/concept_guides/fsdp_and_deepspeed",[217],[274],{"type":192,"value":275},"FSDP vs DeepSpeed 对比",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":277,"children":279},{"id":278},"megatron-core万亿参数模型的训练框架",[280],{"type":192,"value":281},"Megatron-Core：万亿参数模型的训练框架",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":283,"children":284},{},[285],{"type":192,"value":286},"Megatron-Core 是 NVIDIA 专为万亿参数模型设计的训练框架，提供张量并行（层内切分，适合单节点多卡）、流水线并行（层间切分，适合多节点）、序列并行（长序列场景降低激活显存）的原生实现。通过 8 路张量并行和 8 路流水线并行，可在 1024 张 A100 上训练 175B 参数的 GPT-3 模型。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":288,"children":289},{},[290,291,298,299,306,307],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":292,"children":295},{"href":293,"rel":294},"https://github.com/NVIDIA/Megatron-LM",[217],[296],{"type":192,"value":297},"Megatron-LM GitHub",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":300,"children":303},{"href":301,"rel":302},"https://docs.nvidia.com/megatron-core/developer-guide/latest/user-guide/parallelism-guide.html",[217],[304],{"type":192,"value":305},"Megatron 并行策略指南",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":308,"children":311},{"href":309,"rel":310},"https://developer.nvidia.com/blog/scaling-language-model-training-to-a-trillion-parameters-using-megatron/",[217],[312],{"type":192,"value":313},"万亿参数训练",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":315,"children":317},{"id":316},"acceleratehugging-face-分布式封装",[318],{"type":192,"value":319},"Accelerate：Hugging Face 分布式封装",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":321,"children":322},{},[323],{"type":192,"value":324},"Accelerate 是 Hugging Face 提供的分布式训练封装库，让单卡代码几乎零改动扩展到多卡/多机。只需几行代码即可完成模型、优化器、数据加载器的分布式准备。支持 DeepSpeed、FSDP、Megatron 等多种后端，提供统一的配置界面，是研究实验快速迭代的利器。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":326,"children":327},{},[328,329,336,337],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":330,"children":333},{"href":331,"rel":332},"https://huggingface.co/docs/accelerate/index",[217],[334],{"type":192,"value":335},"Accelerate 文档",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":338,"children":341},{"href":339,"rel":340},"https://github.com/huggingface/accelerate",[217],[342],{"type":192,"value":343},"Accelerate GitHub",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":345,"children":347},{"id":346},"分布式训练选择指南",[348],{"type":192,"value":346},{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":350,"children":351},{},[352],{"type":192,"value":353},"模型规模决定并行策略：\u003C 7B 单卡或 DDP 足够，7B-70B 使用 FSDP 或 DeepSpeed ZeRO-3，70B+ 需要 Megatron-Core 配合多种并行组合。场景偏好：研究/实验推荐 Accelerate + FSDP 快速迭代，生产部署选择 DeepSpeed 功能全面，超大规模训练使用 Megatron-Core 配合 NVIDIA 优化。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":355,"children":356},{},[357,358,365,366],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":359,"children":362},{"href":360,"rel":361},"https://sumanthrh.com/post/distributed-and-efficient-finetuning/",[217],[363],{"type":192,"value":364},"分布式训练完整指南",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":367,"children":370},{"href":368,"rel":369},"https://llamafactory.readthedocs.io/en/latest/advanced/distributed.html",[217],[371],{"type":192,"value":372},"LLaMA-Factory 分布式",{"title":178,"searchDepth":374,"depth":374,"links":375},2,[376,377,378,379,380],{"id":197,"depth":374,"text":200},{"id":240,"depth":374,"text":243},{"id":278,"depth":374,"text":281},{"id":316,"depth":374,"text":319},{"id":346,"depth":374,"text":346},"markdown","content:6.maps:_ai:operations:distributed.md","content","6.maps/_ai/operations/distributed.md","6.maps/_ai/operations/distributed","md",[388,392],{"_path":389,"title":390,"description":391},"/maps/_ai/operations/data-processing","Data Processing","AI 数据处理技术与最佳实践，包括 NeMo Curator、Ray Data、MinHash + LSH 等工具和方法。",{"_path":393,"title":394,"description":395},"/maps/_ai/operations/infrastructure","Infrastructure","AI 基础设施与云平台，包括 Modal、Lambda Labs、SkyPilot 等 Serverless GPU 和多云编排方案。",1772185506325]